data.description: The "Land of Opportunity" awaits at this property! This nearly 10 acre ranch style home has 3 bedrooms and 3.5 baths (there is also a bedroom located in the lower level with a built-in fire escape). The house has over 4,000 square feet  including both levels. The open floor plan will "WOW" you as it contains living, dining and great room areas (with a stone fireplace)! The large kitchen is an entertainers dream and all appliances stay with the home! The owners suite has a private bath and walk-in closet. Wood floors adorn nearly the entire main level.  This is one floor living at its best with main level laundry and a convenient  half bath for guests. The home is handicap accessible (wide hallways and stairwells) and it offers a chairlift located in the garage as well as a house power generator. The newly and fully finished basement is so spacious with a large recreation area, storages rooms, bedroom and full bath. The exterior of the home features a spacious deck and a large front porch at entry.  Updates and improvements include : Full Finished Basement (2023), New Refrigerator and updates to kitchen appliances, Roof (2013), Washer & Dryer (2018), Whole House Waterproofing (around 2014), Water tank (2016), Improvements to the geothermal heating and cooling system (w/humidifier)....the list is numerous. With almost 10 acres to roam, the possibilities are endless! Make sure you tour this one asap! You won't be disappointed!
